---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Delete Account & Data — Zeroed"
  description="Learn how to delete your Zeroed app data, disconnect Google Drive sync, and manage your purchase history."
>
    <article class="legal-page">
        <header class="legal-hero">
            <div class="container"><h1>Delete Account & Data</h1></div>
        </header>
        <div class="legal-body">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="highlight">
                    <p><strong>Zeroed is a Local-First App</strong></p>
                    <p>Unlike traditional apps, Zeroed does not have a central account system. Your data is stored on your device, giving you complete control.</p>
                </div>

                <h2>How to Remove Your Data</h2>

                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3><span class="step-num">1</span> Local Data (On Your Device)</h3>
                    <p>All budget data, transactions, and categories are stored locally in an encrypted database.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Uninstall the app</strong> — deletes all locally stored data automatically.</li>
                        <li><strong>Clear app data</strong> — Settings &rarr; Apps &rarr; Zeroed &rarr; Clear Data.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="warning">Once deleted, local data cannot be recovered unless backed up on Google Drive.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3><span class="step-num">2</span> Google Drive Sync (If Enabled)</h3>
                    <p>If you use cross-device sync, an encrypted copy lives in your Google Drive.</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Sign out from Google in Zeroed's settings.</li>
                        <li>Revoke Zeroed's access at <a href="https://myaccount.google.com/permissions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Account Permissions</a>.</li>
                        <li>Delete the <code>ZeroedData</code> folder from your Google Drive.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>

                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3><span class="step-num">3</span> Purchases (RevenueCat)</h3>
                    <p>Purchase records are tied to your Apple ID or Google Play account. Manage subscriptions through your device settings.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3><span class="step-num">4</span> Desktop Licenses (Lemon Squeezy)</h3>
                    <p>Check your email for the original purchase receipt from Lemon Squeezy. Use the license management link to deactivate or transfer.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="contact-card">
                    <h2>Need Assistance?</h2>
                    <p>If you have any questions about data deletion, we're here to help.</p>
                    <a href="mailto:support@stillwareltd.com" class="btn-primary">Email Support</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</Layout>

<style>
    .legal-hero {
        padding: 12rem 0 3rem;
        background: var(--gradient-obsidian);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .legal-hero h1 { color: #ffffff; font-size: 3rem; }

    .legal-body {
        padding: 3rem 0 6rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .legal-body h2 { margin-top: 2.5rem; font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .legal-body p { margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; }
    .legal-body ul, .legal-body ol { margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
    .legal-body li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .legal-body code { background: var(--color-surface); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em; }
    .legal-body a { color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: underline; }

    .highlight {
        background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.04);
        padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .step-card {
        background: var(--color-surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .step-card h3 {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .step-num {
        width: 28px;
        height: 28px;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: var(--color-primary);
        color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 50%;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .warning {
        background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08);
        border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }

    .contact-card {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 3rem;
        background: var(--gradient-obsidian);
        border-radius: 20px;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .contact-card h2 { color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0; }
    .contact-card p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
</style>
